with the Army, who had taken over the, who had these 
political officers, I guess you'd call them, that

30:54.636 --> 31:18.167
took over

30:54.636 --> 31:18.167
the supervision of the government of the 
Burgermeister.

31:18.187 --> 31:20.230
And we had a liaison with them. And then we, of 
course, had this air base. We had some of the German

31:23.958 --> 31:34.549
people there that worked there and continued 
working.

